<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- فَإِنْ أَعَانَهُ غَيْرُهُ؛<span class="c5"> كَكَوْنِ رَأْسِهِ فِي المَاء وَنَحْوِهِ:</span> لَمْ يَحِلَّ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٤]</span> وَقَوْلُ بِاسْمِ اللهِ عِنْدَ تَحْرِيكِ يَدِهِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- وَتَسْقُطُ سَهْواً، لَا جَهْلاً.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَذَكَاةُ جَنِينٍ خَرَجَ مَيِّتاً وَنَحْوَهُ:</span> بِذَكَاةِ أُمِّهِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَكُرِهَتْ:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- بِآلَةٍ كَالَّةٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- وَحَدُّهَا <span class="c2">(١)</span> بِحَضْرَةِ مُذَكًّى.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- وَسَلْخٌ وَكَسْرُ عُنُقٍ قَبْلَ زُهُوقٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- وَنَفْخُ لَحْمٍ لِبَيْعٍ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَسُنَّ:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- تَوْجِيهُهُ إِلَى القِبْلَةِ، عَلَى شِقِّهِ الأَيْسَرِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- وَرِفْقٌ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> بِهِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- وَتَكْبِيرٌ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) في (د): وسنها.<br>(٢) هنا نهاية النسخة (ب).</p> </div>